===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{term|fre||lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{m|ang|frÄ“o}}, {{etyl|gem-pro|en}} {{m|gem-pro|*frijaz}}, from {{etyl|ine-pro|en}} {{m|ine-pro|*prei-||to be fond of}}, {{m|ine-pro|*prey-}}. Compare West Frisian {{term|frij|lang=fy}}, Dutch {{term|vrij|lang=nl}}, Low German {{term|free|lang=nds}}, German {{term|frei|lang=de}}, Danish {{term|fri|lang=da}}.

The verb comes from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{m|ang|frÄ“oÄ¡an}}.

