===Etymology===
From {{etyl|la|en}} {{m|la|encyclopaedia}}, from {{etyl|grc|en}} {{m|grc|á¼Î³ÎºÏÎºÎ»Î¹Î¿Ï‚ Ï€Î±Î¹Î´ÎµÎ¯Î±||the circle of arts and sciences, curriculum}}, from {{m|grc|á¼Î³ÎºÏÎºÎ»Î¹Î¿Ï‚||circular, rounded, round}}, from {{m|grc|ÎºÏÎºÎ»Î¿Ï‚||circle}} + {{m|grc|Ï€Î±Î¹Î´ÎµÎ¯Î±||the rearing of a child, education}}, from {{suffix|Ï€Î±Î¹Î´ÎµÏÏ‰|Î¯á¾±|t1=rear a child|nocat=yes|lang=grc}}, from {{m|grc|Ï€Î±á¿–Ï‚||child}}.

